			<div class="content" id="post-content-2068579">
									

<p>Well, not <em>literally</em>. I <em>literally</em> just typed a document and mentioned lots of groups.</p>
<p>Seriously, though, you have to figure that every group has lists like this somewhere. If anything, the Foundation probably has separate databases for it. But this is designed to both expound upon the relationships between ORIA and the other GoIs, as well as the relationship between ORIA and the rest of the Iranian government and between ORIA and House Afseneh. And lay down the foundation for some future stuff.</p>
<p>I mean, this is a series of events that happened over the course of a year (annual request). A lot can happen in a year, involving a lot of different groups.</p>

